#### Facebook and LinkedIn
Make sure to use **@Udacity** and **#selfdrivingudacity** in your posts!

<html>

<head>
<style>
.fb {color: white;
  background-color: #4661b0;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-weight: bold;
  height: 28px;
  font-size: 14px;}
.fb:hover {color: #4661b0;
  background-color: white;
  border-color: #4661b0;
  transition: background-color 0.4s}
.linkedin {color: white;
  background-color: #0077B5;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-weight: bold;
  height: 28px;
  font-size: 14px;}
.linkedin:hover {color: #0077B5;
  background-color: white;
  border-color: #0077B5;
  transition: background-color 0.4s}
</style>

</head>

<body>
<form action="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?">
  Enter the full URL of your Github repository or Youtube video:<br>
  <input type="url" name="u" placeholder="Paste URL here">
  <input type="hidden" name="hashtag" value="#selfdrivingudacity">
  <button class="fb">Share on Facebook</button>
</form>

<form action="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true">
  <input type="url" name="url" placeholder="Paste URL here">
  <input type="hidden" name="title" value="Advanced Lane Finding">
  <input type="hidden" name="summary" value="I finished Advanced Lane Finding in the Self-Driving Car Nanodegree @udacity #selfdrivingudacity">
  <button class="linkedin">Share on LinkedIn</button>
</form>

</body>

</html>
